				h1.ar-heading.kx-bg.f-oku.wtxt what is KNOX's skill?
				.col-md-6
					p.ar-text Although KNOX keeps a number of metahumans on the payroll, he has no superpowers himself. A vengeful coward, Knox hides inside an armored powersuit and behind a small army of brainless goons. Don't mistake this cowardace for kindness - KNOX has leveraged his wealth and power to steal relics from the gods and execute superheroes in the streets. KNOX's MINION ability allows players to hide behind their henchmen while crafting horrible plots to strike at your enemy's heart!

					p.ar-text So how does MINION work? Some Utilities in your deck have the MINION skill. When a Utility with MINION is in play, you may destroy that card to prevent one instance of damage dealt to you directly. By playing Utilities with MINION, Knox can avoid big chunks of damage without relying on other methods stay in the game. You can even get rid of multiple MINIONS in one turn if you find yourself under attack!
