						p.ar-text Cannon Fodder is a Utility card available in Knox's deck. Played by itself, it has no card text other than MINION. Anytime you would take damage, you may destroy this card instead.
						br
						p.ar-text Moronic Gangster is a Utilty card available in Knox's deck. Played by itself, it has no card text other than MINION. Anytime you would take damage, you may destroy this card instead.
						br
						p.ar-text Cannon Fodder and Moronic Gangster are two of many Utilities from KNOX's deck with the MINION skill. That means whenever you have one of these cards in play, you can destroy one of them to block damage dealt to you directly. Since MINIONS only prevent individual instances of damage, it's a good idea to have multiple MINIONS in play to keep yourself safe.
						br
						p.ar-text Throw It Into A Portal is great at getting rid of pesky Utilities while Barrage goes directly for your opponent. This versatility is GRAVITY GIRL's greatest strength, especially since you can further mix-and-match abilities by choosing which Utilities to destroy.
