				p.ar-text Playing Knox will require you to choose which of your MINIONS live and die. Many of Knox's Utilities are very aggressive and Knox can offer lots of support to those MINIONS via his Actions and Feats. Want to help KNOX take over the world? Focus on keeping three Utilities in play at all times in order to keep the pressure up. Draw as many cards as it takes to make secure your ultimate victory!

